settings.description: I wanted to do a very complete level 0-0

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.

This is a replica of the very first Level of "Plok!" for the SNES. Also, its a test to see how well this editor was and to be honest, is kinda frustrating, but thats expected for a project in Alpha.
A remake of Super Mario World 1-3. The rotating chain platforms aren't in SMB3, so several SMB1 Platforms have been added to help you collect coins.
